<p class="lead">The Association is governed by a volunteer Board of Directors. To protect continuity across board transitions, we publish <strong>role-based</strong> contacts rather than personal email addresses — messages reach whoever currently holds each office.</p>

<h2>Reach the Board</h2>
<div class="contact-grid">
  <div class="contact"><div class="role">President</div><div class="email"><a href="mailto:{{ site.email.president }}">{{ site.email.president }}</a></div><p class="note">Presiding officer of the Association.</p></div>
  <div class="contact"><div class="role">Secretary</div><div class="email"><a href="mailto:{{ site.email.secretary }}">{{ site.email.secretary }}</a></div><p class="note">Records, minutes, and member records requests.</p></div>
  <div class="contact"><div class="role">Treasurer</div><div class="email"><a href="mailto:{{ site.email.treasurer }}">{{ site.email.treasurer }}</a></div><p class="note">Assessments, budget, and financial matters.</p></div>
  <div class="contact"><div class="role">Board of Directors</div><div class="email"><a href="mailto:{{ site.email.board }}">{{ site.email.board }}</a></div><p class="note">General correspondence to the full Board.</p></div>
</div>

<h2>General &amp; resident contacts</h2>
<div class="contact-grid">
  <div class="contact"><div class="role">General inquiries</div><div class="email"><a href="mailto:{{ site.email.info }}">{{ site.email.info }}</a></div><p class="note">Questions about the community or this website.</p></div>
  <div class="contact"><div class="role">Owner / resident support</div><div class="email"><a href="mailto:{{ site.email.support }}">{{ site.email.support }}</a></div><p class="note">Help with your account, contact info, or a community issue.</p></div>
</div>

<h2>Emails you may receive from the Association</h2>
<div class="contact-grid">
  <div class="contact"><div class="role">Community announcements</div><div class="email">announcements@vlscoa.org</div><p class="note">Community-wide announcements. You can unsubscribe from these.</p></div>
  <div class="contact"><div class="role">Statutory notices</div><div class="email">notices@vlscoa.org</div><p class="note">Official statutory notices to owners. By law, you cannot unsubscribe from these.</p></div>
</div>

<div class="callout">
  <p style="margin:0"><span class="k">Managing agent.</span> The Association works with a professional managing agent for day-to-day operations. Routine maintenance and account matters can also be routed through <a href="mailto:{{ site.email.support }}">{{ site.email.support }}</a>, and the current managing-agent contact is listed on the <a href="/management-certificate/">Management Certificate</a>.</p>
</div>

<p class="note">A dedicated Association mailing address and phone line are being established and will be published here and on the Management Certificate once available.</p>
